  "prompt": "How do i get NBA 2K17 Redeem Code?",
  "response": "To get a redeem code for NBA 2K17, you can try the following methods:\n\n1. **Promotions and Sales**: Occasionally, retailers or gaming platforms run promotions where you can get a redeem code for NBA 2K17 with your purchase of the game or related merchandise.\n\n2. **Social Media and Giveaways**: Follow the official NBA 2K social media channels. They sometimes host giveaways and contests where you could win redeem codes.\n\n3. **Online Forums and Communities**: Join gaming forums, subreddits, or communities focused on NBA 2K. Members sometimes share codes or information on how to acquire them.\n\n4. **Sales from Official Stores**: Check platforms like Xbox Live, PlayStation Store, or Steam during sales events. Sometimes they offer discounts or bundles which may include redeem codes.\n\n5. **Game Bundles**: Keep an eye out for any special bundles or editions of the game being sold by retailers that may include additional content or redeem codes.\n\nAlways ensure you are obtaining codes from legitimate sources to avoid scams.",
